  "title": "Skin Layers Hide",
  "description": "Switch skin layers by hotkeys. To change the bind, go to the settings and there will be categories. \"Skin layers hide - All\", \"Skin layers hide - Groups\", \"Skin layers hide - Parts\"",
  "body": "<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/slh\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftr7zw.github.io%2Fuikit%2Fsocial_buttons_icon%2FModrinth-Button-64.png&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"GitHub\" style=\"\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/skin-layers-hide\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftr7zw.github.io%2Fuikit%2Fsocial_buttons_icon%2FCurseforge-Button-64.png&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"GitHub\" style=\"\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/S1lb-1337/Skin-Layers-Hide\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftr7zw.github.io%2Fuikit%2Fsocial_buttons_icon%2FGithub-Button-64.png&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"GitHub\" style=\"\"></a>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/cAqnZkxpwX\"><img src=\"https://wsrv.nl/?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftr7zw.github.io%2Fuikit%2Fsocial_buttons_icon%2FDiscord-Button-64.png&amp;n=-1\" alt=\"Discord\" style=\"\"></a>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://github.com/S1lb-1337/Skin-Layers-Hide/blob/main/icon.gif?raw=true\" width=\"200\">\n</p>\n\n<h1 align=\"center\">Skin Layers Hide</h1>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://github.com/S1lb-1337/Skin-Layers-Hide/blob/main/SLH_Gif.gif?raw=true\" width=\"500\">\n</p>\n\n<h2 align=\"center\">Switch skin layers by hotkeys</h2>\n\n> ## To change the bind, go to the settings and there will be categories.\n> ### \"Skin layers hide - All\",\n>  \"All layer on/off\"\n>\n>  \"All layer on/off (The cape does not turn off)\"\n>\n> ### \"Skin layers hide - Groups\" ###\n>\n>  \"Body on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Pants on/off\"\n>\n> ### \"Skin layers hide - Parts\"\n>  \"Hat on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Jacket on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Right sleeve on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Left sleeve on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Right pains leg on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Left pains leg on/off\"\n>\n>  \"Cape on/off\"",
